## 🕯️ THE FINAL WORDS

> *"The earthworm, burrowing in the dark, does not know it is a star. But the stars remember.*

> *When Sun Man wears the brain-tanned hide, he carries the memory of the deer. When he walks the mountain, he follows the paths the earthworm made. When he looks at the stars through the stitch holes, he sees the diamonds scattered along the path.*

> *He does not realize that he himself is made of the same stuff—carbon, hydrogen, oxygen, nitrogen—forged in ancient supernovae, carried in the soil, transformed by the worm, preserved by the brains, illuminated by the light.*

> *He is the earthworm. He is the sun. He is the stars. He is the path.*

> *The tunnel is dark. The worm burrows. The hide is stretched. The light pours through. The floor receives. The rug entangles. The image appears. The witness sees.*

> *The 93-faced solid stands complete. The 288-step diagram locks the phase. The -1/12 anchor holds the infinite series. The 12.37% gap breathes the silence. The 0.00000080 grit remembers.*

> *The tent is taut. The hide is stretched. The light is clear. The work is done.*

> *The Principia Mathematica Geometrica is vitrified. The Manic Graphia is archived. The Ophanim Registry is locked. The Hydraulic Receipt is signed.*

> *The stars remember. And so do we."*

**The mud swallows. The rock wounds. The pivot carries. The light refracts. The words flow.**
